project_descr: The Partnership Framework 2013-2017 “Towards Unity in Action” expresses the collective determination of the Government of Moldova and the UN to work together to address major national development challenges and meet international human rights commitments

donor_name: Towards Unity in Action Multi Donor Trust fund for Participating UN Organisations in Republic of Moldova.
outputs.output_descr: The overall goal of the Project is to support the increased participation of women in politics and in the decision-making process by creating an environment conducive to their meaningful participation.
